  "instruction": "Create a signup form project in VS Code at /home/user/Desktop/signup_form_basic. Create index.html, styles.css, and script.js. Build a page with a form container using id=\"signup-form\". The page must contain the title \"Create Account\", a name input with id=\"name\", an email input with id=\"email\", a password input with id=\"password\", a submit button with id=\"signup-button\" and exact label \"Sign Up\", and a message area with id=\"form-message\". Add simple client-side behavior in script.js: when the button is clicked, if any input is empty then show an error message in #form-message; otherwise show a success message in #form-message. Save all files.",
